name: Ascension
description: In the void of the metaverse, creations roam ceaselessly. Not unlike stars and galaxies, most of them we will never get to see. However, should we come across an object in a perpetual motion of ascension, we recognize their strive. One can even imagine that every dim sparkle is an entity waiting to be recognized. Ascension .. an ode to rising artists of the metaverse.
